      "content": "but that feels so fake. like, \"small moments of hope\" doesn't change the fact that the math doesn't add up. how can anyone be expected to just keep living normally, working jobs and making plans, when the entire foundation of the world is crumbling? it feels like staying is just prolonging the inevitable suffering for no reason. it almost feels more honest to just... not participate in a dying system.",
